{
  "stem": "21310.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, there was-- had to be some kind of an organization or government who was coordinating things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I think the Judenrat tried as best as it could.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not personally, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's-- you know, we hated the police, not so much in the beginning when they were just police-- traffic and for minor infractions.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But towards the end, like in 1942, when they were taking [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 6,000, 8,000, and 10,000 people a day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so they were cooperating with the German, trying to catch these people or coming and blocking off-- I mean, not the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Germans would, would block off a street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all that people had come down from the apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they would check the cards, work cards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At that time, you could only stay in the ghetto if you worked for the German-- for one of those factories.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- or for the Judenrat of for the police.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, and if you didn't, and if you caught, you were sent, sent away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I-- we had to move again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, from [INAUDIBLE] we moved to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we moved to another place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we worked for, worked for [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Schultz, ?] which was-- if you know it was like a factory like Schindler, only the man who owned it was a German.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But he wasn't, wasn't as, as good as Schindler.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was factory with furs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were making fur jackets and stuff like that for the army on the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we were able to work for [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Schultz. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, the ghetto was divided into self-contained compounds.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like labor camp, actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we, we worked in this factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
